cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.MM

This paper deals with cooperative wireless networks and physical layer security, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also discusses eavesdropping and security (cs.CR), and proposes optimization schemes for achieving secrecy (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper presents numerical results and simulations (cs.MM) to illustrate the proposed solutions. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.IT and cs.NI, followed by cs.CR, cs.SY, and cs.MM.
